	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The 283 figure might refer to the portion of the NES scanline inside the NTSC production aperture, which includes the NES's left and right borders and the nominal analog blanking (<a href="http://lurkertech.com/lg/video-systems/#480i" class="postlink">production aperture minus clean aperture</a>) but excludes NTSC horizontal blanking.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


